headline: CSX (CSX) Lags Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: CSX (CSX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -8.11% and 1.59%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: 1 Oversold Stock Set for a Comeback and 2 to Avoid
